title: Organic Chemistry Laboratory
description: Continuation of CHEM 43A, 143A, 43AM, and 143AM, emphasizing synthetic methods of organic chemistry. Enrollment is limited to majors in the Department of Chemistry and Biochemistry unless space is available. A materials fee is required. Prerequisites: CHEM 43A, 143A, 43AM or 143AM, and CHEM 40B or 140B.
